item.title: About
item.description: I’m Carter, and this is my blog. Some of the posts here will be about technical things, and others will be about completely non-technical things that are also (hopefully) interesting (to somebody besides me). Here’s are some facts about me: I have a thing for lists. No, seriously. They’re like, hands down my favorite way to present information. I’m from Spokane, and right now I live in San Francisco. I graduated from Dartmouth’s CS program in 2017.

item.title: Contact
item.description: Feel free to reach out with questions, comments or concerns at carter.bastian1@gmail.com or use the buttons at the top of the site to find me on ~the internet~ Please feel free to check my work. If I write something that’s wrong or misleading, let me know and I’ll correct it and credit you for helping me find the mistake :)
